text: Brauninidae is a monotypic family of trematodes in the order Diplostomida. It consists of one genus, Braunina Heider, 1900,Heider, K. (1900). Über Braunina, ein neues Genus aus der Gruppe der Hemistomidae. Verhandlungen der Deutschen Zoologischen Gesellschaft, Leipzig, 19–22. which consists of one species, Braunina cordiformis Wolf, 1903. ==References== Category:Diplostomida Category:Trematode families
title: Brauninidae
